{"tid":1966242,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"而家輸緊呀！仲唔繼續做就前功盡棄喇！入泥同我睇下要做咩！","createTime":"2020-04-10T04:55:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-12T05:38:21.000Z","uid":308879,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ac4f55121d395c71c7b98ec353d8c43e83ce8907","tid":1966242,"uid":308879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T04:55:24.000Z","msg":"話說小弟有幫手做飲食界選民登記，多得好多巴打絲打協助，D黃店基本上都掃過晒，同埋都登記得七七八八。但係其實都而家都仍然係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>輸到仆街</strong></span></span>呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解？你自己查下D黃藍MAP，谷極黃店都係得果<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">2000幾間</span></span></strong>，仲未計<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">分店又無票</span></span></strong>，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">拎會所牌既食肆又無票</span></strong></span>，<span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">食環街市入面既食肆又無票</span></strong></span>，<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>老闆唔係持牌人又無票</strong></span></span>⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n連對家張宇人都笑9我地冇L用<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>目前，公民黨和多名素人都有意乘着「黃色經濟圈」的概念參選。可是，面對對手的來勢洶洶，現任議員張宇人今日卻表示不擔心，反指受疫情影響，飲食業生意大受影響，「而家去諗選舉的，是否不去諗業界生死？」</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢過去幾屆選舉，拎住<strong><span style=\"color: brown;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2500張鐵票</span></span></strong>，佢心諗係立法會佢瞓到百年歸老都仲得呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以，大家要<strong><span style=\"color: maroon;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">繼續搶攻搶攻再搶攻</span></span></strong>！<br />\n<br />\nX你！咩唔係過左截止日期喇咩？搶條毛呀？<br />\n<br />\n施主，你實在太年輕了！4月2日只係舊選民更改資料既截止日期，仲有另一個截止日期係 5月2日呀！<br />\n<br />\n即係話，如果食肆既食牌係<span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">公司登記</span></strong></span>，或者係<strong><span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">從來沒做過選民既個人登記</span></span></strong>，都<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仲未截止</span></span></strong>！<br />\n<br />\n所以，我地下一步就係要專攻唔係多係公司登記又唔係太能夠高調表態既暗黃店，咁你即係講乜L野呢？<br />\n即係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">茶飲店、樓上 Cafe、教烘焙既教室、西式烘焙店同埋酒吧</span></span>！<br />\n呢類店店主後生多，黃既機會大，又畀政府搞到甘，10個有8個都唔會想投廿蚊張，所以唔理藍黃，全部都問就岩架喇！<br />\n<br />\n點問法呢？好簡單，同我<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">轟炸</span></strong></span>佢地Facebook/IG就得！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地已經預備左<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">「飲食界選民登記生成器」</span></span></strong><br />\n只要老闆入晒呢堆資料畀我地，我地有專人將一份填好既表格送到上門，老闆一簽名就得！<br />\n<br />\n「公司持牌」版<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/Nh3qHpnKhUdhHXcr5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FNh3qHpnKhUdhHXcr5&d=GkP5J4C4AUyWsqXHyTPi6wUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=9f0f4956\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/Nh3qHpnKhUdhHXcr5</a><br />\n<br />\n「個人持牌」版<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/NmWDjXcFyjAmk8EQ9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FNmWDjXcFyjAmk8EQ9&d=GkP5J4C4AUyWsqXHyTPi6wUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=6baa80d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/NmWDjXcFyjAmk8EQ9</a><br />\n<br />\n而家得返一個月唔夠，同我快快手做野喇！"},{"pid":"18994efadbb12ae64af0d648f86008ab896ebdff","tid":1966242,"uid":2